      "body": "**SOLVED (supersedes the earlier \"two v4.31 sorrys remain hard\" memory): both `rawPushPullMap_comp` (Cech) and `pullback_cast_compat` (GR) are now proved sorry-free.**\n\n- **`CechHigherDirectImage.lean` `rawPushPullMap_comp`**: final transport is pure **term-mode**, no `rw` (avoids \"motive not type correct\"). Shape: `(congrArg (fun t => (pushforward p\u2081).map A_head \u226b t) he).trans (((Functor.map_comp _ _ _).symm.trans (congrArg (pushforward p\u2081).map ((Category.assoc _ _ _).trans INNER))).trans (Functor.map_comp _ _ _))`. `he` rewrites the outer over-triangle `eqToHom` to `(pushforward p\u2081).map eqInner`; `Category.assoc` fixes `(x\u226by)\u226bz` vs `x\u226b(y\u226bz)` before `INNER`; `map_comp` folds/splits.\n\n- **`GlueDescent.lean` `pullback_cast_compat`**: proved from the associativity solved-forms. Recipe: (1) `set_option backward.isDefEq.respectTransparency false in` BEFORE the docstring (the `pullbackComp` solved-forms unfold to the `\u22d9`-object form; else v4.31 transparency wall blocks matching). (2) tagged `pullbackComp_inv_comp_map_inv_app` + `pullbackComp_inv_comp_congr_hom_app` `@[reassoc]`. (3) phase-1 `simp only [pullbackComp_comp_fst_hom_app, pullback_map_inv_comp_hom_app_assoc, pullback_map_congr_inv_comp_hom_app_assoc, pullbackComp_inv_comp_congr_hom_app_assoc, pullbackComp_inv_comp_map_inv_app(_assoc), Category.assoc]` keeping congr as casts. (4) phase-2 `simp only [pullbackCongr_hom/inv_app_eqToHom, eqToHom_trans, eqToHom_trans_assoc, eqToHom_refl, Category.assoc, comp_id, id_comp]` (need `eqToHom_trans_assoc` for mid-chain). Variance: `pullbackComp x y : pullback y \u22d9 pullback x \u2245 pullback (x\u226by)`.\n\n- Iterate via `lake build <module>` reading the unsolved-goal state (LSP dead).",
